OL,3,CMan pleads guilty over post trolling
OL,4,CWest Brom supporter's death
OL,6,FA Sheffield Wednesday fan who posted
OL,7,Fon social media about the death of a
OL,8,Frival supporter has pleaded guilty to
OL,9,Fsending offensive communications.
OL,11,FRichard Crisp, 55, was arrested after
OL,12,Fappearing to mock the death of West
OL,13,FBromwich Albion fan Mark Townsend.
OL,15,FMr Townsend, 57, suffered a medical
OL,16,Femergency in the Leppings Lane end and
OL,17,Flater died when the two sides met at
OL,18,FHillsborough on 28 September.
