OL,3,CMan pleads guilty over post trolling
OL,4,CWest Brom supporter's death
OL,6,FAfter the match, Crisp appeared to
OL,7,Fmake a link to the 97 Liverpool fans
OL,8,Fwho died at the Hillsborough disaster
OL,9,Fin 1989.
OL,11,FHe wrote: "What are we at now, 98?
OL,12,FWhen we get to 100 we'll have a party."
OL,14,FCrisp, from Hillsborough, was charged
OL,15,Fwith sending an indecent or offensive
OL,16,Fcommunication.
OL,18,FHe admitted the charge when he
OL,19,Fappeared at Sheffield Magistrates
OL,20,FCourt on Monday and will be sentenced
OL,21,Fat a later date.
