OL,6,FAsked whether he had anything to say
OL,7,Fto Mr Townsend's family as he left
OL,8,Fcourt, Crisp said: "Not at this stage."
OL,10,FCrisp has already been banned from
OL,11,FSheffield Wednesday for life after the
OL,12,Fclub condemned his "abhorrent social
OL,13,Fmedia post".
OL,15,FIn a statement at the time the club
OL,16,Fsaid: "We condemn absolutely this
OL,17,Foutrageous behaviour and underline our
OL,18,Fzero tolerance policy towards unlawful
OL,19,Factivity on all social media
OL,20,Fplatforms."
